{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962290/extras/CR_ecran_titre.gif?t=1729631567\" /><br>What else are the <strong>Gormnoq</strong> up to?<br>Break into their lair, progress to the King and retrieve what they've stolen.<br><br>Chained Runes is a <strong>deckbuilding </strong>game with <strong>runes</strong> that focuses on <strong>reflection </strong>and <strong>anticipation</strong>.<br>Place them as best you can in your <strong>chain</strong> to <i>optimize</i> their effects. <i>Analyze </i>your opponents and <i>anticipate </i>their actions to move forward.<br><i>Discover </i>the different runes, abilities and talents, and create an optimized deck to defeat all the Gormnoqs in your path and reach the king.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962290/extras/CR_chaine.gif?t=1729631567\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Strategic battles, rich in possibilities</strong></h2>Get your brain working. Chained Runes requires a good dose of <strong>reflection</strong>, <strong>anticipation </strong>and <strong>analysis</strong>.<br>Battles revolve around 3 elements:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Runes</strong>: the game's main mechanic, place them in your chain to play their effects successively.<br></li><li><strong>Abilities</strong>: allow you to play an effect instantly, available only 1x per turn.<br></li><li><strong>Talents</strong>: Passives that play effects when their trigger's condition occurs.</li></ul><br>Find synergies to optimize your turns and unleash your true power.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962290/extras/CR_battle.gif?t=1729631567\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Customize your Codex</strong></h2>Choose 3 <strong>Arcanes</strong> from the 5 available.<br>Each Arcane specializes in one aspect of the battle system <i>(Offensiveness, Survival, Wounds, Aura, Runes)</i> and has its own set of associated runes, abilities and talents.<br>Mix and match as you want to play the way that suits you best.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962290/extras/CR_bibliotheque.gif?t=1729631567\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Unexpected encounters</strong></h2>Scour the lair's <strong>3 floors</strong>, encountering a variety of wacky Gormnoqs room after room.<br>Be on the lookout for <strong>special encounters</strong> scattered around each floor. Chests, tougher enemies and much more.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962290/extras/CR_rencontre.gif?t=1729631567\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Take up the challenge!</strong></h2>The King is not so easily approached. Don't expect to gain power with every defeat.<br><strong>Discover</strong> and <strong>learn</strong> everything you can do in <i>Chained runes</i>. Optimize what you've learned to go further and further.<br>The game has a <strong>fixed difficulty</strong>, so it's up to you to master it enough to see it through.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962290/extras/CR_facing_all.gif?t=1729631567\" /><br><i><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>The game is made with a very small team. The English localization is not done by a professional third party, so expect approximations and mistakes... . Sorry about that.</strong></li></ul></i>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Etage #2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2962290/f0bcf172261dfa49ec25bc5ba2d721bfbd37c54c.jpg"},{"name":"Etage #3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2962290/5684598bfc2e20cb0f2bb986a9b3fc1e526c5a7a.jpg"},{"name":"Arc-en-ciel","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2962290/4e3c6040